WQ">Vương Xương Linh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/T%E1%BA%B7ng-%C4%90inh-D%E1%BB%B1c/poem-Z_PpO1_rG-tl9DAKFT4lyw">Tặng Đinh Dực - 贈丁翼</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/author-3mdeOfneLQCMOxlLrV12_w">Tào Thực</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%C3%ADch-Ng%C3%B4-S%E1%BB%9F-l%C6%B0u-bi%E1%BB%87t-Ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-s%E1%BB%A9-qu%C3%A2n-l%C6%B0u-h%E1%BA%ADu-ki%C3%AAm-m%E1%BA%A1c-ph%E1%BB%A7-ch%C6%B0-c%C3%B4ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-li%E1%BB%85u-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-VusrYuqrkvq24lkjJ2HUYQ">Tương thích Ngô Sở, lưu biệt Chương sứ quân lưu hậu kiêm mạc phủ chư công, đắc liễu tự - 將適吳楚，留別章使君留後兼幕府諸公，得柳字</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/%E1%BB%A8c-t%C3%ADch-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-P6xtQk8fCZudef4S0B9eeQ">Ức tích kỳ 2 - 憶昔其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
